title: We have a beautiful 2 bedroom apartment waiting fore you! Call us!
posting_body: ['City Limits Apartments is located less than 10 miles south from the vibrant city of Minneapolis, Minnesota.', 'Our community is nestled in the Windom neighborhood close to I-35 and MN-121.', 'Enjoy living in a community that is just a few minutes from shopping, entertainment, and dining!', 'At City Limits Apartments, residents can enjoy a variety of outdoor amenities including a playground, community picnic and BBQ areas, and beautiful landscaping.', 'We also have laundry facilities on each floor of our buildings.', 'Our 1 and 2 bedroom apartments have electric kitchen appliances, a balcony, multiple closets, and much more!', "We know it's important to you so we made sure that all of our apartments are ready for high-speed Internet and cable.", 'We bundle certain utilities into the rent including heat, gas, trash, and sewer.', 'Our community combines affordable apartments, a wonderful location, and excellent management to create a great rental experience.', 'We want our apartment to become your new home.', 'City Limits Apartments is owned and managed through Monarch Investment and Management Group.', '-Convenient Access To Stairways', '-High-Speed Internet and Cable Available', '-Air Conditioning Unit', '-Community Picnic and Barbecue Areas', '-Controlled Access', '-Playground With Slides and Jungle Gym', '-Electric Kitchen Appliances', '-Private Balcony', '-Courtyard', '-Spacious Living Room and Dining Room', '-Neutral Decor', '-Well-Lit Galley Style Kitchens', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 9AM-6PM', '127 E 59th St, Minneapolis, MN 55419', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
